    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-11-30T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-11-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="653" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d653">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Constantinople</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-11-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 30,
                                    1895</hi>
                        </date>. (Received Dec. 18.)</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 698.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform you that it is
                            deemed most prudent to delay making a formal demand for payment of loss
                            sustained by the burning of missionary property at Harpoot and Marash
                            until a full statement of the amount of damages sustained is made and
                            your answer to this dispatch by telegram is received. It is not probable
                            that the amount of actual values destroyed will be known here before
                            this reaches you. * * *</p>
                <p>It is hoped that facts showing values destroyed will be fully known when
                            this has reached you, and before acting I will await your telegraphic
                            instructions.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">A. W. Terrell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
